      "type": "callout_bar",
      "color": "#00D26A",
      "label": "Officially Supported:",
      "html": " VirtualBox with Kali Linux installed from ISO. Other hypervisors (VMware, Parallels, UTM) may work but you\u2019re responsible for your own troubleshooting."
    },
